1
00:00:38,340 --> 00:00:41,010
[Adapted from the novel
Sweet Sixteen by Zi Yue]

2
00:00:41,010 --> 00:00:44,340
[Sweet Sixteen]

3
00:00:44,340 --> 00:00:47,340
[Episode 16]

4
00:00:48,380 --> 00:00:49,540
Have you ever considered

5
00:00:50,940 --> 00:00:53,300
the possibility
of you having another family?

6
00:00:57,380 --> 00:00:58,220
It's not important.

7
00:00:58,220 --> 00:00:59,660
I'm very happy with the life I have now.

8
00:01:01,380 --> 00:01:03,300
What if they want to see you?

9
00:01:08,300 --> 00:01:09,260
What are you trying to say?

10
00:01:10,500 --> 00:01:11,460
I want to make sure

11
00:01:12,100 --> 00:01:13,780
this matter won't hurt you.

12
00:01:19,260 --> 00:01:20,020
It's fine.

13
00:01:20,540 --> 00:01:21,860
No matter what happens,

14
00:01:21,860 --> 00:01:22,900
we'll face it together.

15
00:01:25,540 --> 00:01:27,340
I need to see
someone important tomorrow.

16
00:01:27,660 --> 00:01:28,740
If it goes well,

17
00:01:29,380 --> 00:01:30,740
I'll tell you everything.

18
00:01:36,980 --> 00:01:37,700
Zhang,

19
00:01:38,260 --> 00:01:39,780
am I too old?

20
00:01:40,420 --> 00:01:41,540
Don't say that.

21
00:01:42,220 --> 00:01:43,380
I think I can't

22
00:01:44,260 --> 00:01:46,020
control Qu Weiran anymore.

23
00:01:46,460 --> 00:01:47,140
Mr. Qu.

24
00:01:48,940 --> 00:01:50,380
Thank you for agreeing to see me.

25
00:01:51,140 --> 00:01:54,420
Should I call you Rita or Miss Shu?

26
00:01:54,700 --> 00:01:56,660
That's not important.

27
00:01:57,140 --> 00:01:59,020
More importantly, I've wanted
to see you for a long time.

28
00:01:59,460 --> 00:02:00,260
What is this about?

29
00:02:00,580 --> 00:02:01,500
Let me hear it.

30
00:02:02,300 --> 00:02:03,180
I heard

31
00:02:03,900 --> 00:02:05,220
you're allergic to mangoes.

32
00:02:07,420 --> 00:02:08,140
Mr. Qu,

33
00:02:08,900 --> 00:02:09,780
you have a grandson.

34
00:02:10,470 --> 00:02:11,400
[Project Collaboration Agreement]

35
00:02:13,260 --> 00:02:13,980
Mr. Qu.

36
00:02:21,700 --> 00:02:23,820
So this is the reason she came to Haide?

37
00:02:33,060 --> 00:02:34,740
What brought you here, Mr. Qu?

38
00:02:43,300 --> 00:02:44,380
Where were you today?

39
00:02:44,580 --> 00:02:46,260
Do I need to report
my whereabouts to you?

40
00:02:48,580 --> 00:02:49,860
You're not going to invite me up?

41
00:02:50,660 --> 00:02:52,260
My small house

42
00:02:52,260 --> 00:02:54,020
is no place for someone like you.

43
00:02:54,500 --> 00:02:56,060
Why don't you invite me
to your place next time?

44
00:02:58,460 --> 00:02:59,100
Why?

45
00:03:00,300 --> 00:03:01,540
You want to relive

46
00:03:02,700 --> 00:03:03,660
some memories with me?

47
00:03:04,340 --> 00:03:05,620
That's up

48
00:03:05,860 --> 00:03:08,100
to whether you have the guts
to take me home.

49
00:03:28,700 --> 00:03:29,500
What is it?

50
00:03:32,780 --> 00:03:33,700
What is it?

51
00:03:33,700 --> 00:03:34,740
Who upset you?

52
00:03:37,340 --> 00:03:38,700
Why are you looking at me?

53
00:03:40,020 --> 00:03:41,460
Can you stay away from Qu Weiran?

54
00:03:42,180 --> 00:03:43,420
It's not what you think.

55
00:03:43,420 --> 00:03:44,620
Then what is it, Shu Yawang?

56
00:03:47,780 --> 00:03:49,060
Do you have to do this to yourself?

57
00:03:58,420 --> 00:04:00,620
I've never thought of
trying to make it up to you.

58
00:04:01,100 --> 00:04:02,780
I was very upset
about losing Tang Xiaotian

59
00:04:04,100 --> 00:04:05,660
but I just like him.

60
00:04:06,580 --> 00:04:08,340
I cannot lose you.

61
00:04:13,660 --> 00:04:14,780
After all these years,

62
00:04:15,300 --> 00:04:18,180
it's been you who's been by my side
through the best and worst times,

63
00:04:18,660 --> 00:04:19,860
through despair and hope.

64
00:04:20,460 --> 00:04:21,980
I finally understand it now.

65
00:04:22,900 --> 00:04:24,740
The most important person to me

66
00:04:25,700 --> 00:04:27,180
has always been by my side.

67
00:04:27,380 --> 00:04:28,900
Because I love you.

68
00:04:28,900 --> 00:04:30,540
♪Want to be closer♪

69
00:04:31,860 --> 00:04:35,780
♪But the distance between us♪

70
00:04:36,940 --> 00:04:38,060
Your happiness

71
00:04:38,820 --> 00:04:40,420
gives meaning to my existence.

72
00:04:41,580 --> 00:04:43,100
From the past to the future,

73
00:04:43,100 --> 00:04:44,500
♪As unclear as if
we were looking through mist♪

74
00:04:44,500 --> 00:04:45,860
the person I want to protect

75
00:04:45,860 --> 00:04:47,140
♪Asking myself♪

76
00:04:47,140 --> 00:04:48,260
has only been you.

77
00:04:48,660 --> 00:04:49,820
♪Why♪

78
00:04:49,820 --> 00:04:52,340
♪Can't I forget?♪

79
00:04:52,340 --> 00:04:53,260
I love you too.

80
00:04:53,540 --> 00:04:56,700
♪The answer has always been you♪

81
00:04:58,060 --> 00:05:01,060
♪The reason my heart beats♪

82
00:05:02,060 --> 00:05:05,860
♪If being together♪

83
00:05:06,500 --> 00:05:09,700
♪Is the final ending♪

84
00:06:06,500 --> 00:06:07,260
Mr. Qu,

85
00:06:07,900 --> 00:06:09,500
you're meeting them this afternoon.

86
00:06:09,780 --> 00:06:11,380
It's still too early.

87
00:06:12,140 --> 00:06:13,460
I'm late.

88
00:06:17,940 --> 00:06:18,620
Dad.

89
00:06:18,860 --> 00:06:20,020
You're in a good mood.

90
00:06:26,860 --> 00:06:27,500
Leave.

91
00:06:28,020 --> 00:06:29,500
I don't want to see you today.

92
00:06:30,620 --> 00:06:32,940
So you're waiting for
the grandson you've never met.

93
00:06:34,220 --> 00:06:34,740
You...

94
00:06:35,900 --> 00:06:36,980
How did you know?

95
00:06:38,980 --> 00:06:40,420
I've been with you for so many years.

96
00:06:41,740 --> 00:06:43,300
If I had no improvement,

97
00:06:44,540 --> 00:06:46,220
how could I take over Haide Enterprises?

98
00:06:47,180 --> 00:06:49,060
I used Shu Yawang to agitate Xia Mu

99
00:06:49,460 --> 00:06:50,860
for him to injure me.

100
00:06:51,700 --> 00:06:53,620
After all, we are related to Xia Mu.

101
00:06:54,100 --> 00:06:55,820
I knew exactly what he would do.

102
00:06:56,420 --> 00:06:58,580
Then I sent him to prison,

103
00:06:59,820 --> 00:07:03,340
destroying
your grandson's life.

104
00:07:04,140 --> 00:07:05,780
However, I paid a price for it too.

105
00:07:07,340 --> 00:07:09,180
The sun will always set,

106
00:07:09,180 --> 00:07:09,980
Dad.

107
00:07:11,700 --> 00:07:13,060
You should retire

108
00:07:13,340 --> 00:07:14,780
and enjoy the rest of your years.

109
00:07:23,220 --> 00:07:25,660
Everything I have is thanks to you.

110
00:07:26,180 --> 00:07:27,100
Don't worry.

111
00:07:27,620 --> 00:07:28,900
In the future,

112
00:07:29,860 --> 00:07:30,900
I will repay you

113
00:07:30,900 --> 00:07:32,300
for raising me.

114
00:07:52,980 --> 00:07:54,060
Shu Yawang.

115
00:08:05,020 --> 00:08:05,940
Shu Yawang!

116
00:08:10,170 --> 00:08:12,350
[To Shu Yawang: Where did you go?]

117
00:08:24,300 --> 00:08:25,770
[Shu Yawang: I need to take care of
something in the office, I'm working.]

118
00:08:33,500 --> 00:08:35,900
[Xia Mu:
Okay, I'll bring lunch for you.]

119
00:08:35,900 --> 00:08:36,600
[To Xia Mu: Okay.]

120
00:08:48,900 --> 00:08:49,540
Mr. Qu,

121
00:08:50,020 --> 00:08:50,820
she's awake.

122
00:08:57,180 --> 00:08:58,820
♪SO RE MI♪

123
00:08:59,940 --> 00:09:04,300
♪I can't help thinking♪

124
00:09:04,820 --> 00:09:08,100
♪A happy or sad ending♪

125
00:09:09,580 --> 00:09:12,900
♪Is up to us♪

126
00:09:13,340 --> 00:09:17,100
♪Lovers are always forced to part♪

127
00:09:18,100 --> 00:09:21,020
♪How dramatic♪

128
00:09:22,300 --> 00:09:25,580
♪Doing my best to run to you♪

129
00:09:26,220 --> 00:09:31,260
♪And our happy ending♪

130
00:09:31,740 --> 00:09:34,060
♪If I can meet you again♪

131
00:09:34,380 --> 00:09:36,340
♪And write this story again♪

132
00:09:36,780 --> 00:09:40,300
♪I don't believe in fate♪

133
00:09:41,220 --> 00:09:43,700
♪If I can hug you again♪

134
00:09:44,140 --> 00:09:45,460
♪I don't care♪

135
00:09:45,460 --> 00:09:48,780
♪About the bitter past♪

136
00:09:49,420 --> 00:09:51,540
♪Let all our partings♪

137
00:09:51,540 --> 00:09:53,620
♪Indifference and struggles♪

138
00:09:53,620 --> 00:09:56,900
♪Return to when we met♪

139
00:09:57,540 --> 00:10:00,540
♪As the crowd disappears♪

140
00:10:00,980 --> 00:10:02,300
♪It's still you♪

141
00:10:02,300 --> 00:10:08,660
♪Watching the sunset with me♪

142
00:10:09,700 --> 00:10:12,260
♪If we start again♪

143
00:10:12,260 --> 00:10:14,700
♪Can our ending be changed?♪
